    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3504277/" class="title-link">切莫为了取悦别人而迷失了自己</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3504277"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zhouliyun0923/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1817618-60.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zhouliyun0923/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Evanthe</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
